{"tid":1808667,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應增委員位置予落選建制派報道　政府稱名單仍擬備中","createTime":"2020-01-02T13:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T14:54:29.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53dfd235932f8418530fed6bb4c340b1a1cbfd9a","tid":1808667,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500740-20200102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500740-20200102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPtAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=47dbabd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500740-20200102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=21f28588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500740-20200102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n對於有報道指，民政處在各分區委員會，增加315位予區議會選舉落敗的建制派人士，可能繞過區議會搞政治宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署回覆查詢時表示，現屆分區委員的任期至今年3月31日，新一屆分區會委員的名單仍在擬備中，數目尚待確定，並無相關報道所說的情況。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，分區會的委員來自社會各階層，政府在委任時會考慮多項因素，包括有關人士的經驗、才能、專業知識、對地區事務的認識、服務社區的熱誠及組織社區活動的能力等，從不同途徑吸納有志服務社會的合適人士。"},{"pid":"e0c3aa740468a96ca192e382456442a96a9f460f","tid":1808667,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"政府幫手整埋制裁名單咁體貼"},{"pid":"d184220efe518605ddfc22842fdc2805893033b9","tid":1808667,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"反對，呢個要出黎遊行"},{"pid":"7f8b7b5287e406f5fd76887a35900320086b4754","tid":1808667,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}